name: MetaMe
description:
Mi experiencia con la comunidad NFT ha sido un gran impacto en mi vida: me siento ligado, por innumerables razones, a personas que nunca he visto en persona. Pareciera que esos lazos nos han dado un sostén nuevo, un grupo de nodos que interactuamos y compartimos cosas imposibles de registrar. 
--------------------
My experience with the NFT community has been a great impact on my life: I feel connected, for countless reasons, to people I have never met in person. It seems that these connections have given us a new support, a group of nodes that we interact with and share things unregistrable.

Visual work: Blender
Audio: Ableton Live
1920x1080
